Description: lightweight PyQt6 file manager for Linux
 linux-file-manager is a lightweight file manager written in Python and PyQt6.
 It provides common file browsing workflows, bookmarks, trash integration,
 previews, search, archive extraction, tagging, and a basic hidden-folder vault.
